| -- | -- | -- |
| 1  | 3  | 5  |
| 2  | 4  | 6  |

```
m1 ge 4;
```

| #0    | #1    | #2   |
| ----- | ----- | ---- |
| false | false | true |
| false | true  | true |

```
m2=6..1$2:3;
m2;
```

| #0 | #1 | #2 |
| -- | -- | -- |
| 6  | 4  | 2  |
| 5  | 3  | 1  |

```
m1>=m2;
```

| #0    | #1    | #2   |
| ----- | ----- | ---- |
| false | false | true |
